Jason, 

I see what you mean. However, one of our goals in JUnit 4 was to remove the
recursive composition of tests. It is difficult to explain and difficult to
support properly in test runners. What I need is an example of JUnit 4-style
dynamic test case creation.

Sincerely yours,

Kent Beck
Three Rivers Institute

